1. *Jedanput* sam se probudio u sred noći. (I woke up once in the middle of the night.)
2. Nisam *jedanput* ponovio istu grešku. (I didn't repeat the same mistake just once.)
3. Ona dolazi *jedanput* nedeljno u posetu. (She comes to visit once a week.)
4. *Jedanput* kada sam bio na odmoru, upoznao sam zanimljive ljude. (Once when I was on vacation, I met interesting people.)
5. Želim da *jedanput* probam tezgu na pijaci. (I want to try the market stall once.)
6. *Jedanput* sam se izgubio u ovom delu grada. (I got lost once in this part of town.)
7. *Jedanput* kada sam bio mali, zatražio sam autogram od poznatog glumca. (Once when I was little, I asked a famous actor for an autograph.)
8. *Jedanput* sam prekršio pravilo i dobio sam kaznu. (I broke a rule once and got punished.)
9. Nećeš uspeti *jedanput* da naučiš sve. (You won't be able to learn everything in just one go.)
10. *Jedanput* kad dođeš ovamo, moraš da probaš našu nacionalnu hranu. (Once you come here, you have to try our national food.)